CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

April 30, 2008

[Cite as 04/3012008 Case Announcements, 2008-0hio-2014.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2008-0367. Duke Energy Ohio, Inc. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, Nos. 03-93-EL-ATA, 03-2079-EL-AAM, 03-2081-EL-AAM, and 03-2080-EL-ATA. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of the motion for leave to intervene of Duke Energy Ohio *1484and the motion for leave to intervene of Duke Energy Retail Sales, LLC,

It is ordered by the court that the motions are granted.
